name: Valar
author: musl
description: Meant as an experiment to test latest techniques implemented on traiNNer, including: AdaTarget, KernelGAN, UNet discriminator, nESRGAN+ arch, noise patches, camera noise, isotropic/anisotropic/sinc blur, frequency separation, contextual loss, mixup, clipL1 pixel loss, AdamP optimizer, etc. The config file is provided on the download link above. I encourage everybody to mirror the model, distribute and modify it in anywway you want.
dataset: Hand selected 1471 Raw images from the Adobe-MIT 5k dataset, processed using Rawtherapee.
